## Scope

The MIT text above applies to **original** work in this repository (for example
code under `src/`, `web/`, and `deploy/`). It does **not** apply to trees under
`third_party/`, or to fonts and binary media under `assets/` that may have
their own terms.

See **THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md** for bundled components and how they are licensed.

A **WebAssembly** build that links GPL-covered libraries may itself need to
follow **GPL** rules for the combined program. Read **THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md**
and get legal advice if you plan to distribute that binary.
